### Tüm ürünleri getir — JOIN sorgusu
GET http://localhost:5155/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Id ile getir
GET http://localhost:5155/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### Fiyat aralığına göre filtrele
GET http://localhost:5155/api/products/price?min=10&max=100
Accept: application/json

### Kategori bazında istatistik — GROUP BY
GET http://localhost:5155/api/products/stats
Accept: application/json

### Yeni ürün ekle
POST http://localhost:5155/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Monitor",
  "price": 349.99,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### Güncelle
PUT http://localhost:5155/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "price": 1299.99
}

### Sil
DELETE http://localhost:5155/api/products/1